l/Bienne]]\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 2\n| date       = 5 September 1937\n| time       = \n| team1      = [[FC Biel-Bienne|Biel-Bienne]]\n| score      = 1 \u2013 3\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28088 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| goals1     = Baur {{goal||pen. 1:2}}\n| goals2     = {{goal|12|0:1}} [[Othmar Saner|Saner]]<br />{{goal||0:2}} [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]]<br />{{goal||1:3}} [[Ren\u00e9 Schaller|Schaller]]\n| stadium    = [[Gurzelen Stadion]], [[Biel/Bienne]]\n| attendance = 1,700\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Hans W\u00fcthrich]] [[Bern]]\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 3\n| date       = 12 September 1937\n| time       = 15:00\n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| score      = 4 \u2013 0\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28089 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Lausanne-Sport|Lausanne-Sport]]\n| goals1     = [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]] {{goal|2|1:0}}<br />[[Othmar Saner|Saner]] {{goal|7|2:0}}<br />[[Numa Monnard|Monnard]] {{goal||3:0}}<br />[[Numa Monnard|Monnard]] {{goal||4:0}}\n| goals2     = \n| stadium    = [[Landhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = 3,500\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Jaggi [[Bern]]\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 4\n| date       = 26 September 1937\n| time       = 15:00\n| team1      = [[FC Nordstern Basel|Nordstern Basel]]\n| score      = 4 \u2013 2\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28090 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| goals1     = Br\u00fcckler {{goal||1x}}<br />Mohler {{goal||1x}}<br />Forelli {{goal||1x}}<br />B\u00fcche {{goal||1x}}\n| goals2     = {{goal||2x}} [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]]\n| stadium    = [[Stadion Rankhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = 8,000\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Hans W\u00fcthrich]] [[Bern]]\n| result     = L\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 5\n| date       = 17 October 1937\n| time       = 15:00\n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| score      = 6 \u2013 1\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28091 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Bern]]\n| goals1     = [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]] {{goal||2x}}<br />[[Ren\u00e9 Schaller|Schaller]] {{goal||1x}}<br />[[Othmar Saner|Saner]] {{goal||1x}}<br />[[Fernand Jaccard|Jaccard]]{{goal||1x}}<br />[[Alfons Weber|Weber]] {{goal||1x}}\n| goals2     = {{goal||1x}} B\u00e4rlocher\n| stadium    = [[Landhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = 3,500\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Meyer [[Lausanne]]\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 6\n| date       = 24 October 1937\n| time       = 15;00\n| team1      = [[Grasshopper Club Z\u00fcrich|Grasshopper Club]]\n| score      = 4 \u2013 2\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28092 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| goals1     = [[Fritz Wagner (footballer)|Wagner]] {{goal|24|1:1}}<br />[[Alfred Bickel|Bickel]] {{goal|45|2:1}}<br />[[Alfred Bickel|Bickel]] \n{{goal|77|3:1}}<br />[[Fritz Wagner (footballer)|Wagner]] {{goal|72|4:1}}\n| goals2     = {{goal|10|0:1}} [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]]<br />{{goal|77|4:2}} [[Othmar Saner|Saner]]\n| stadium    = [[Hardturm]], [[Z\u00fcrich]]\n| attendance = 8,500\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Scherz [[Bern]]\n| result     = L\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 7\n| date       = 21 November 1937\n| time       = 14:30\n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| score      = 2 \u2013 2\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28093 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Grenchen|Grenchen]]\n| goals1     = [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]] {{goal||1x}}<br />[[Alfons Weber|Weber]] {{goal||1x}} \n| goals2     = {{goal||2x