07 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| goals1     = Karcher {{goal||1x}}\n| goals2     = {{goal||2x}} o.g.<br />{{goal||2x}} [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]]<br />{{goal||1x}} [[Guglielmo Spadini|Spadini]]<br />{{goal||pen. 1x}} [[Fritz Schmidlin|Schmidlin (I)]]\n| stadium    = [[Stadion Allmend]], [[Luzern]]\n| attendance = 2,300\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Lutz [[Geneva]]\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 22\n| date       = 15 May 1938\n| time       = 15:00\n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| score      = 0 \u2013 0\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28108 Summary]\n| team2      = [[BSC Young Boys|Young Boys]]\n| goals1     = \n| goals2     = \n| stadium    = [[Landhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = 4,500\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Spengler [[Olten]]\n| result     = D\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 12\n| date       = 29 May 1938\n| time       = \n| team1      = [[SC Young Fellows Juventus|Young Fellows Z\u00fcrich]]\n| score      = 3 \u2013 1 \n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28098 Summary]\n| team2      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| goals1     = [[Leopold Kielholz|Kielholz]] {{goal||1:0}}<br />[[Leopold Kielholz|Kielholz]] {{goal|14|2:0}}<br />Deriaz {{goal|48|3:1}}\n| goals2     = {{goal|38|2:1}} [[Eduard Buser|Buser]]\n| stadium    = [[Letzigrund]], [[Z\u00fcrich]] \n| attendance = 1,000\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Allemann [[Biel/Bienne]]\n| result     = L\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n\n==== League table ====\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|show_limit=5\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=LUG|name_LUG=[[AC Lugano|FC Lugano]]\n|team2=GCZ|name_GCZ=[[Grasshopper Club Z\u00fcrich]]\n|team3=YB |name_YB =[[BSC Young Boys]]\n|team4=BAS|name_BAS=[[FC Basel]]\n|team5=NOR|name_NOR=[[FC Nordstern Basel]]\n|team6=LS |name_LS =[[Lausanne Sports]]\n|team7=SER