ary]\n| team2      = {{flagicon|SUI}} [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| goals1     = {{goal||1:1}}<br />{{goal||2:1}}<br />{{goal||3:2}}\n| goals2     = {{goal||0:1}} [[August Ibach|Ibach]]<br />{{goal||2:2}} [[Guglielmo Spadini|Spadini]]<br />{{goal||3:3}} [[Alfons Weber|Weber]]<br />{{goal|75|3:4}} [[Alfons Weber|Weber]]<br />{{goal||4:5}} [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]]\n| stadium    = Terrain des Havre AC, [[Le Havre]]\n| attendance = 6,000\n| referee    = \n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = End of season \n| date       = 12 June 1938\n| time       = \n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]] {{flagicon|SUI}}\n| score      = 6 \u2013 3\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28086 Summary]\n| team2      = {{flagicon|FRA}} [[FC Metz|Metz]]\n| goals1     = [[Guglielmo Spadini|Spadini]] {{goal|20|1:1}}<br />[[August Ibach|Ibach]] {{goal|39|2:2}}<br />[[Numa Monnard|Monnard]] {{goal|44|3:2}}<br />[[Guglielmo Spadini|Spadini]] {{goal|55|4:2}}<br />[[Numa Monnard|Monnard]] {{goal|81|5:3}}<br />[[August Ibach|Ibach]] {{goal||pen. 6:3}}\n| goals2     = {{goal||0:1}}<br />{{goal||1:2}}<br />{{goal||o.g. 4:3}} [[Heinz Els\u00e4sser|Els\u00e4sser]]\n| stadium    = [[Landhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = 500\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}}\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\n}}\n\n=== Nationalliga ===\n{{main|1937\u201338 Nationalliga}}\n\n==== League matches ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| round      = Round 1\n| date       = 29 August 1937\n| time       = 16:00\n| team1      = [[FC Basel|Basel]]\n| score      = 1 \u2013 0\n| report     = [https://www.fcb-archiv.ch/saison/spiele?command=detail&id=28087 Summary]\n| team2      = [[SC Young Fellows Juventus|Young Fellows Z\u00fcrich]]\n| goals1     = [[Numa Monnard|Monnard]] {{goal|80|1:0}}\n| goals2     = \n| stadium    = [[Landhof]], [[Basel]]\n| attendance = 2,498\n| referee    = {{flagicon|SUI}} Allemann [[Biel/Bienne]]\n| result     = W\n| stack      = yes\